data.description: Want to spend more time at home and less time commuting? Well, prepare to fall in love with this beautiful open and spacious 2 bedroom condo in Dupont! This is a ground-floor unit with an attached garage in a terrific community. White shaker cabinets in the kitchen and fun accent walls throughout! The home offers both a dining area and eat-in kitchen space. In the summer you can relax on your patio while HOA handles the lawn maintenance for you or enjoy all the trails the community has to offer. Only minutes to JBLM and I5, and lots of local shopping and dining. What are you waiting for? Make an appointment today.
